Name: Enoki
About the game: Mushrooms - combine some of the characteristics of plants and animals. Fungi are present in all ecological niches - in water and on land, in soil and on all kinds of other substrates. Our task is to solve puzzles, collect coins and make three rows. Game features Enoki Mushroom Control Ability to move objects Keys, Switches and Levers Many interesting quests Match 3 puzzles Collecting coins
